
Numbers:

(range: 0 – 10)
0 – nol
1 – ozn
2 – do
3 – tri
4 – vad
5 – vid
6 – ses
7 – sev
8 – okt
9 – non
10 – zye

(range: 11 – 19)
11 – zyeozn
12 – zyedo
13 – zyetri
14 – zyevad
15 – zyevid
16 – zyeses
17 – zyesev
18 – zyeokt
19 – zyenon

(range: 20 – 29)
20 – dozye
21 – dozyenov
22 – dozyedo
23 – dozyetri
24 – dozyevad
25 – dozyevid
26 – dozyeses
27 – dozyesev
28 – dozyeokt
29 – dozyenon

(range: 30 – 90)
30 – trizye
40 – vadzye
50 – vidzye
60 – seszye
70 – sevzye
80 – oktzye
90 – nonzye

(range: 100 - 120 [n%10])
100 – ozndan
110 – ozndanzye
120 – ozndandozye



(range: 10E+2 – 10E+33)
ozndan     – 100
oznmil     – 1,000
oznmilzen  – 1,000,000
oznvilzen  – 1,000,000,000
ozntrilzen – 1,000,000,000,000
oznvadlzen – 1,000,000,000,000,000
oznvidlzen – 1,000,000,000,000,000,000
oznseslzen – 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000 
oznsevlzen – 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000
oznoktlzen – 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000
oznnonlzen – 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000
oznzelzen  – 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000
oznazelzen – 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000




